<div id="review_2172317137" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2172317137" />
    <a title="Lark of The Bookwyrm&#39;s Hoard" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard"><img alt="Lark of The Bookwyrm&#39;s Hoard" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1359500529p2/9080084.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2172317137?book_show_action=true">Nov 04, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lark of The Bookwyrm&#39;s Hoard" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lark of The Bookwyrm&#39;s Hoard" href="/user/show/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard">Lark of The Bookwyrm&#39;s Hoard</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/6589970-red-lily">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=contemporary-romance">contemporary-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=backlist-reader-2017">backlist-reader-2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=own">own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=kindle">kindle</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=romantic-suspense">romantic-suspense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=re-read">re-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9080084-lark-of-the-bookwyrm-s-hoard?shelf=paranormal">paranormal</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2172317137" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16141945695988793934">Probably 3.5 stars on this one. The ghost story kept ramping up through each book, and in this one it moves into possession. I enjoyed the main characters but felt the ending was a little abrupt, maybe even a little flat after all that buildup. And I did kind of hope David would end up with someone, too. Review to come.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


